query:
SELECT name, nameEn, type, category, gender, religion, website, 
       CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO' END as has_desc,
       CASE WHEN features IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO' END as has_features
FROM schools 
WHERE description IS NOT NULL OR features IS NOT NULL OR studentCount IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 10;
